data.name: label7.Text
data.value: If this setting is checked this software will automatically write ID3 tags including title/artist/album etc to the generated MP3 file header. By default tags are ID3 v1. But if any of the attributes mentioned overflows(normally more than 30 characters) the encoding engine will automatically switch to ID3 v2 tags

data.name: label6.Text
data.value: Click on the image left to get the typical volume control dialog of windows. With this dialog you can set the proper mixer device and its volume. To function properly RaagaHacker needs that the volume of the wave output is set properly in the recording properties.
